46.000Z","msg":"跟本係垃圾地黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T03:54:57.000Z","msg":"亞洲一日唔做人口管制一日都係死<br />\n結果就係得top果堆移到去白人國家果班無事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648555beb28c1e92ceac5c5f38671b44d8ee483b","tid":989423,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T04:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}